    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rusting on the rocker panels, several large dents, and clear coat failure across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, and several interior components, including the radio and rear window motors, are non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a noticeable oil leak and a suspension that requires immediate attention. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
