    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and I\u2019ve taken really good care of it. I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
